"Check status" = "检查状态";
"Model service" = "模型服务";
"Runner (WebDriverAgentRunner-Runner)" = "Runner（WebDriverAgentRunner-Runner）";
"Runner address" = "Runner 地址";
"The address used to connect to Runner (port 8100). On iPhone, use http://127.0.0.1:8100." = "用于连接 Runner 的地址（端口 8100）。\n• iPhone 上通常用：http://127.0.0.1:8100\n• 局域网调试可填 iPhone 的 Wi‑Fi IP（需为 Runner 开启 Wireless Data）";
"Service URL (Base URL, OpenAI-compatible)" = "服务地址（Base URL，OpenAI 兼容）";
"Required. Examples:\nDoubao: https://ark.cn-beijing.volces.com/api/v3/responses\nOpenAI: https://api.openai.com/v1" = "必填。示例：\n豆包：https://ark.cn-beijing.volces.com/api/v3/responses\nOpenAI：https://api.openai.com/v1";
"Required. Example: doubao-seed-1-8-251228" = "必填。示例：doubao-seed-1-8-251228";
"Optional if already set on device. Leave empty to keep the existing key." = "如果本机已保存过密钥，这里可留空；留空会继续使用已保存的密钥。";
"Doubao Seed: use Responses. Most OpenAI-compatible services: try Responses first; if unsupported, switch to Chat Completions." = "豆包 Seed：推荐用 Responses。大多数 OpenAI 兼容服务：先试 Responses；不支持再切到 Chat Completions。";
"Use Chat Completions when Responses is unsupported. More compatible, but usually uses more tokens." = "当服务不支持 Responses 时使用 Chat Completions。兼容性更好，但通常更耗 token。";
"Per-step max output (Token)" = "每步最大输出（Token）";
