"Hard stop after this many actions. Prevents runaway loops." = "达到该步数后强制停止，避免任务失控循环。";
"Sleep between executed actions. Increase to reduce flakiness." = "每步动作后等待时间；调大可降低不稳定性。";
"Responses API: max_output_tokens. Larger lets the model think/plan longer." = "Responses API：max_output_tokens。更大可让模型思考/规划更久。";
"Chat Completions: max_completion_tokens. Larger lets the model think/plan longer." = "Chat Completions：max_completion_tokens。更大可让模型思考/规划更久。";
