"Advanced (optional)" = "高级（可选）";
"Reset" = "重置";
"Reset clears local runtime data (logs/chat/screenshots/Notes/token usage); Factory Reset also clears saved settings and the remembered API key; neither affects your model service." = "重置只会清理本机数据，不会影响你的模型服务。\n• 重置运行记录：清空日志/对话/截图/备注/Token 用量；保留已保存的配置。\n• 恢复默认设置：在上面基础上，还会清空已保存的配置（含 API 密钥、自定义系统提示词等）。";
"Reasoning effort (optional)" = "思考强度（可选）";
"Enable Session Cache (Doubao Seed)" = "启用会话缓存（豆包 Seed）";
"Responses only. Enables session caching for doubao-seed models to reduce tokens and improve stability." = "仅限 Responses。为 doubao-seed 模型启用会话缓存，以减少 token 用量并提升稳定性。";
"Half-resolution screenshots" = "半分辨率截图";
"Shrinks screenshots by 50% before sending to the model, reducing Token usage and often speeding up responses." = "发送给模型前将截图缩小一半，以减少 Token 用量并加快响应。";
