"Overlays click/swipe markers on per-step screenshots in Chat." = "在对话中的每步截图上标出点击/滑动等动作位置。";
"Debug raw conversation" = "调试：记录原始对话";
"Stores per-step API request/response JSON (images are placeholders). May contain sensitive info." = "记录每步 API 请求/响应 JSON（图片会用占位符）。可能包含敏感信息。";
